---
title: Crispy Buffalo Tofu Sandwiches with Blue Cheese Dressing, Potato Wedges & Mixed Greens Salad
description: Bright, bold Buffalo sauce and blue cheese dressing elevate this crispy tofu sandwich to delicious new heights. You'll fry up battered tofu and load onto a pillowy buns along with crisp quick-pickled cucumbers. Roasted seasoned potato wedges, plus a mixed green salad with ranch dressing, round out the plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67bc2f51fb63c027ee47259a-50e7defa.jpeg
